Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Focus Five Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:43 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Focus Five Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Focus Five Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. It is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. The fund invests in public equity markets. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. It focuses on factors like potential for long term earnings per share growth, industry developments, regulatory changes, changes in management, and sale or spin-off of a division to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the a blended index comprised of 50% Russell 2500 ...
Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Focus Five Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. It is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. The fund invests in public equity markets. It seeks to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund primarily invests in value stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. It focuses on factors like potential for long term earnings per share growth, industry developments, regulatory changes, changes in management, and sale or spin-off of a division to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the a blended index comprised of 50% Russell 2500 Index, 25% Russell 1000 Index, and 25% MSCI ACWI Ex-US Index. It was formerly known as Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - Gabelli Woodland Small Cap Value Fund. Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Focus Five Fund was formed on December 31, 2002 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


