Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Equity Income Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:43 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Equity Income Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Equity Income Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. It is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in value and dividend paying stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. It invests in securities that have a better yield than the average of the Standard & Poor’s 500 Stock Index and potential for capital gains. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabell...
Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Equity Income Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by GAMCO Investors, Inc. It is managed by Gabelli Funds, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It seeks to invest in value and dividend paying stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations. It invests in securities that have a better yield than the average of the Standard & Poor’s 500 Stock Index and potential for capital gains. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. Gabelli Equity Series Funds, Inc. - The Gabelli Equity Income Fund was formed on January 2, 1992 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


